{"tha-ap405:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap405:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap405:0.3":"Mettaguttheraapadana ","tha-ap405:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap405:1.2":"asoko nama pabbato; ","tha-ap405:1.3":"Tatthasi assamo mayham, ","tha-ap405:1.4":"vissakammena mapito. ","tha-ap405:2.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap405:2.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap405:2.3":"Nivasayitva pubbanhe, ","tha-ap405:2.4":"pindaya me upagami. ","tha-ap405:3.1":"Upagatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap405:3.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap405:3.3":"Paggayha sugatapattam, ","tha-ap405:3.4":"sappitelam apurayim. ","tha-ap405:4.1":"Datvanaham buddhasetthe, ","tha-ap405:4.2":"sumedhe lokanayake; ","tha-ap405:4.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap405:4.4":"bhiyyo hasam janesaham. ","tha-ap405:5.1":"Imina sappidanena, ","tha-ap405:5.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap405:5.3":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap405:5.4":"labhami vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap405:6.1":"Vinipatam vivajjetva, ","tha-ap405:6.2":"samsarami bhavabhave; ","tha-ap405:6.3":"Tattha cittam panidhitva, ","tha-ap405:6.4":"labhami acalam padam. ","tha-ap405:7.1":"‘Labha tuyham suladdham te, ","tha-ap405:7.2":"yam mam addakkhi brahmana; ","tha-ap405:7.3":"Mama dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap405:7.4":"arahattam bhavissati. ","tha-ap405:8.1":"Vissattho hohi ma bhayi, ","tha-ap405:8.2":"adhigantva mahayasam; ","tha-ap405:8.3":"Mamanhi sappim datvana, ","tha-ap405:8.4":"parimokkhasi jatiya’. ","tha-ap405:9.1":"Imina sappidanena, ","tha-ap405:9.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap405:9.3":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap405:9.4":"labhase vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap405:10.1":"Imina sappidanena, ","tha-ap405:10.2":"mettacittavataya ca; ","tha-ap405:10.3":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap405:10.4":"devaloke ramissasi. ","tha-ap405:11.1":"Atthatimsatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap405:11.2":"devaraja bhavissasi; ","tha-ap405:11.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap405:11.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap405:12.1":"Ekapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap405:12.2":"cakkavatti bhavissasi; ","tha-ap405:12.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap405:12.4":"jambumandassa issaro. ","tha-ap405:13.1":"Mahasamuddovakkhobho, ","tha-ap405:13.2":"duddharo pathavi yatha; ","tha-ap405:13.3":"Evamevam ca te bhoga, ","tha-ap405:13.4":"appameyya bhavissare. ","tha-ap405:14.1":"Satthikoti hirannassa, ","tha-ap405:14.2":"cajitva pabbajim aham; ","tha-ap405:14.3":"Kim kusalam gavesanto, ","tha-ap405:14.4":"bavarim upasankamim. ","tha-ap405:15.1":"Tattha mante adhiyami, ","tha-ap405:15.2":"chalangam nama lakkhanam; ","tha-ap405:15.3":"Tamandhakaram vidhamam, ","tha-ap405:15.4":"uppajji tvam mahamuni. ","tha-ap405:16.1":"Tava dassanakamoham, ","tha-ap405:16.2":"agatomhi mahamuni; ","tha-ap405:16.3":"Tava dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap405:16.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap405:17.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap405:17.2":"sappim buddhassadasaham; ","tha-ap405:17.3":"Etthantare nabhijane, ","tha-ap405:17.4":"sappim vinnapitam maya. ","tha-ap405:18.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap405:18.2":"uppajjati yadicchakam; ","tha-ap405:18.3":"Cittamannaya nibbattam, ","tha-ap405:18.4":"sabbe santappayamaham. ","tha-ap405:19.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap405:19.2":"aho no satthu sampada; ","tha-ap405:19.3":"Thokanhi sappim datvana, ","tha-ap405:19.4":"appameyyam labhamaham. ","tha-ap405:20.1":"Mahasamudde udakam, ","tha-ap405:20.2":"yavata nerupassato; ","tha-ap405:20.3":"Mama sappim upadaya, ","tha-ap405:20.4":"kalabhagam na hessati. ","tha-ap405:21.1":"Yavata cakkavalassa, ","tha-ap405:21.2":"kariyantassa rasito; ","tha-ap405:21.3":"Mama nibbattavatthanam, ","tha-ap405:21.4":"okaso so na sammati. ","tha-ap405:22.1":"Pabbataraja himava, ","tha-ap405:22.2":"pavaropi siluccayo; ","tha-ap405:22.3":"Mamanulittagandhassa, ","tha-ap405:22.4":"upanidhim na hessati. ","tha-ap405:23.1":"Vattham gandhanca sappinca, ","tha-ap405:23.2":"annanca ditthadhammikam; ","tha-ap405:23.3":"Asankhatanca nibbanam, ","tha-ap405:23.4":"sappidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap405:24.1":"Satipatthanasayano, ","tha-ap405:24.2":"samadhijhanagocaro; ","tha-ap405:24.3":"Bojjhangabhojano ajja, ","tha-ap405:24.4":"sappidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap405:25.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap405:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap405:25.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap405:26.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap405:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap405:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap405:27.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap405:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap405:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap405:28.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mettagu thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap405:29.1":"Mettaguttherassapadanam tatiyam. "}